25
00:01:28.060 --> 00:01:34.215
Please review material you learned on this subject if you are having trouble keeping up.

26
00:01:34.215 --> 00:01:36.960
Every module will have reading assignments which you can

27
00:01:36.960 --> 00:01:40.675
download from the URL's listed in the class information.

28
00:01:40.675 --> 00:01:45.945
There will be lab assignments for you to perform and online quizzes for you to take.

29
00:01:45.945 --> 00:01:48.445
In module one of course one,

30
00:01:48.445 --> 00:01:52.530
we will give you a high level overview of sensors and actuators as well

31
00:01:52.530 --> 00:01:57.425
as the analog and digital interfaces that connect them to a digital circuit.

32
00:01:57.425 --> 00:02:02.470
